events.title: Rockstar DSP LIVE in Vizag.
events.description:
Rockstar Devi Sri Prasad, the man of high-energy and mass-appeal music, is all set to light up Vizag as the second city of DSP Live India Tour!!! After the electrifying success in Hyderabad, the musical extravaganza now moves to the City of Destiny. Secure your tickets now and gear up for an unforgettable concert experience!


Get ready to Dance, Sing, and Party as Rockstar DSP brings his chart-topping hits and boundless energy to life on stage. Donâ€™t miss the magic! Book your tickets!

events.title: Wonderla Amusement Park, Hyderabad
events.description: Dive into fun at Wonderla Hyderabad, a water park paradise! This award-winning park boasts over 43 rides, with options for all ages and thrill levels. Take a relaxing float down the lazy river, conquer high-speed slides, or scream your heart out on Recoil, India's first reverse looping coaster. Wonderla Hyderabad offers a full day of splashy fun for everyone.
